
COVID-19

In the link below, you will find an interactive infographic about International and Italian (national,regional and provincial)'COVID-19' situation,
created by Alessandro Fossati (me), Giorgio Nardi and Marco Vergani using Tableau platform. 
Data are updated every day automatically and they are downloaded from 'Italian Protezione Civile' GitHub official page.
Have a look here! 

https://public.tableau.com/profile/info.with.data
